  "decision_conditions": [
    "No consent is granted for the proposed graffiti-style artwork on the flank wall fronting Almeida Street and installation of six swan neck lamps. \r\n\r\nThe proposed signs and lamps on the front of the property are in keeping with the discreet style of the surrounding shopfronts and signs. The fascia sign, projecting lamps and the blade sign are not considered to cause demonstrable harm to amenity or public safety. These aspects of the proposal accord are acceptable and therefore accord with the NPPF; Policy CS9 of the Islington Core Strategy (2012); policies DM1 and DM3 of the emerging Development Management Document (2012), and policy Env11 of the Islington Unitary Development Plan (2002).\r\n\r\nConsent is granted for the fascia sign, projecting lamps and the blade sign subject to the following conditions:"
